{"data": {"node": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2099304230107998", "organization": {"id": "1783858331931533", "viewer_permissions": [], "application_groupings": {"nodes": [{"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "1794257190678814"}]}, "id": "604093463411716"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "2099304230107998"}]}, "id": "585815091862240"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "1338585306164362"}]}, "id": "1741024309477537"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "2099304230107998", "release_date": 1554915600, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "2680678705303878"}, "id": "2054250254610184"}]}}, "binary": null, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1571109016, "id": "2385165425134151", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v7", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 5, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "731699601106484"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "2099304230107998"}, "id": "731699601106484", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": null, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "RELEASED", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "2099304230107998", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "390631848424120"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1083559441996718", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Anceder", "keywords": ["shoot", "arcade", "tir", "bullet", "shmup"], "long_description": "Bienvenue dans le shoot-them-up arcade (shmup, bullet hell). Choisissez votre vaisseau et faites le meilleur score possible.\n\nLa mise \u00e0 jour \"MORE\" : Plus de bonus, plus de sons, plus de langues (textes Espagnol & Chinois), plus de fun ! Le mode Fury est d\u00e9sormais plus facile.\n\n- Jouez les 5 mondes \u00e0 la suite pour faire un meilleur score.\n- Musiques originales en HD qui durent le temps des niveaux (pas de boucle r\u00e9p\u00e9titive).\n- Mode normal ou difficile. Vous ferez des scores \u00e9normes en difficile.\n\n- Essayez le mode furie pour plus de vitesse.\n- Optimis\u00e9 pour Oculus Go.\n- Jouable \u00e0 la t\u00e9l\u00e9commande ou au joypad.\n- Scores mondiaux (si connect\u00e9 \u00e0 internet). Vous pouvez mettre des initiales \u00e0 chaque score pour comparer avec vos amis de passage.\n- Vous pouvez jouer allong\u00e9 dans le lit (menu options ou pendant la pause).\n\nUn bug ou id\u00e9e ? Ecrivez \u00e0 cedric@anceder.com ou twitter @ancedergame", "short_description": "Plongez dans le jeu de tir arcade (shmup, shoot'em up, bullet hell). Beaucoup d'action vous attend. \"Insert Coin\" et sautez dans le shmup !"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "220813272336387", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Anceder Go", "keywords": ["shoot", "arcade", "space", "disparo", "shmup"], "long_description": "Bienvenue en al arcade de disparos (shmup, bullet hell). Elige tu nave e intenta hacer el mejor score.\n\nLa actualizaci\u00f3n \"MORE\": \u00a1Con m\u00e1s bonificaciones, m\u00e1s sonidos, m\u00e1s idiomas, m\u00e1s diversi\u00f3n! El modo Furia ahora es m\u00e1s f\u00e1cil.\n\n- Juega los 5 mundos en una fila para obtener un score alto.\n- M\u00fasica original en HD. La m\u00fasica es de nivel completo (sin bucles repetitivos).\n- Modo normal y dif\u00edcil. Har\u00e1s un gran score en el modo dif\u00edcil.\n\n- Prueba el modo furia para un juego a\u00fan m\u00e1s r\u00e1pido.\n- Jugable con joypad o touch.\n- Scores guardados en todo el mundo (si est\u00e1 conectado a Internet). Puedes poner iniciales para cada score, para comparar con tus amigos de pasaje.\n- Puedes jugar acostado en la cama (ver el men\u00fa de opciones o el men\u00fa de pausa).\n\n\u00bfUn error o una idea? Por favor escriba a cedric@anceder.com o twitter @ancedergame", "short_description": "Sum\u00e9rgete en el arcade de disparos (shmup, shoot'em up, bullet hell). Mucha acci\u00f3n te est\u00e1 esperando. \"Insert coin\" y saltar en el shmup!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "1253080834897598", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974721_974452869560672_6962123170564276224_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ui5PUseKYgMQ7kNvgGIP6sO&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC0LU272KxKcBvH3htE3KMcWUuBJAnSOoIJBXI1Ol4aPw&oe=66ED6CAA"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "262912721375200", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982611_2394616770756465_3920028200226258944_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TakhNkxeMuEQ7kNvgGfVGKI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDNXL2Nv8Pd-O-SJMqALebG2Ouz8xkZeOqe5qNdFwLMvw&oe=66ED672E"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "223797378821059", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974788_398562067428946_7248863029855518720_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rGfw8MJrgycQ7kNvgHNs9Ur&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDvoss6eESjBzAPebJ1cdYU7MWYrAOoBs7Mwi9-4BzMDg&oe=66ED6DF7"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "208864823664053", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982589_744642749339588_3090667837820239872_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YXsjjTs67kMQ7kNvgFxaB08&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkX_aj9thToCVe4SBeE1mxUxYUsg6CJqdULhcn1L5Hsw&oe=66ED75EF"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "200812727867259", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031643_492771351576371_4309085141264760832_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qGCEPqL2MUcQ7kNvgF7aTou&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDaO9LX4GjsjhDUG0Kj6yUV6isNzkBoia90TL9PtBOLrw&oe=66ED7121"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "152438239302856", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982620_403891177169121_815638916852875264_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9nRDTy6sFYwQ7kNvgF0myFW&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAvfSIFmoA8S-0oJ5Bay_-XTEWsWzujQaqIvHYLY8xb0g&oe=66ED7832"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "144297240245005", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974717_2302266453215639_9060570528405782528_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5aP5MrUVVvwQ7kNvgERBNa1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBXyty8G2J_UgxnW3z20CObp5tgOu7ys6tbgMjF_aMhnQ&oe=66ED644B"}]}, "id": "214487593000323", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "1167677536908315", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982691_704271173302087_3298892117232844800_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=k8xywU3JCtUQ7kNvgGyCMRP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZUzMk6eQIa1iv1XTphtYXNvf5ghNTmogaaQLcBCVoFw&oe=66ED588B"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "591811674740618", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982688_876759336001512_8999184167161823232_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=E-oDAB5G6rYQ7kNvgHWSYl1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDufM4YyBiGAqjIDQq86hFv21ArckwzE9eVJMnNW2GLjQ&oe=66ED6739"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "582124092514203", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974770_616761398764872_2926226150080380928_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vBBr6V1VqZwQ7kNvgFHQWW0&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA3VTAogGBxKya2M5dYYfqwV3OQREVQFGmBvHqHtM7kkw&oe=66ED4356"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "214507646421385", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974645_820859614941200_7592492187703574528_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ujMlb2soBVYQ7kNvgEciuCf&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDS7eGLGW4jwOVFslOvQP3VE_zzN_8SbdnlSXom5xqUAw&oe=66ED4CE2"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "160732235031751", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974579_2097317323685146_8736316079699132416_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VLZcszCcSI0Q7kNvgE64Gyf&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDimoDrwvvKCl8cPufXCj0TWa5kp5aVaWbIWwP0k3biIg&oe=66ED4E7B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Anceder", "keywords": ["shoot", "arcade", "space", "bullet", "shmup"], "long_description": "Bienvenue in the arcade shoot-them-up (shmup, bullet hell). Choose your ship and try to make the best score.\n\nThe \"MORE\" Update : Now with more bonus, more sounds, more languages (Spanish & Chinese texts), more fun ! The Fury mode is now easier.\n\n- Play the five worlds in a row to make a high score.\n- Original musics in HD. Music are level-long (no repetitive loops).\n- Normal and hard mode. You will make huge scores in hard mode.\n\n- Try the fury mode for an even faster game. \n- Optimized for Oculus Go.\n- Playable with joypad or remote.\n- Scores saved worldwide (if connected to the internet). You can set initials to each score to compare with your visiting friends.\n- You can play lying in bed (see options menu or pause menu).\n\nA bug or idea ? Please write to cedric@anceder.com or twitter @ancedergame", "short_description": "Dive in the arcade shoot-them-up (shmup, shoot'em up, bullet hell). A lot of action is awaiting you. \"